Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a ƙasar Indonesia sun kashe ɗaruruwan mutane kuma har ila ana samun ƙarin mutane
Hukumomi sun sanar a ranar Asabar cewa bayan da wata babbar girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi na Indonesia, mutane 384 suka mutu, da yawa daga cikinsu sun mutu a cikin manyan raƙuman ruwa da suka mamaye rairayin bakin teku.
A ranar Jumma'a, daruruwan mutane sun taru a bakin rairayin bakin teku a birnin Pal, amma da yammacin rana, raƙuman ruwa da suka kai tsawon ƙafa shida sun kai ga bakin teku, sun kashe mutane da yawa kuma sun lalata duk abin da ya hana su yin hakan.
