"Lokacin da ake fuskantar barazanar tsunami a jiya, mutane suna ci gaba da ayyukan da suke yi a bakin rairayin bakin teku kuma ba su gudu ba, saboda haka sun yi fama da bala'i", in ji mai magana da yawun Hukumar Kula da Rashin Bala'i ta Indonesia BNPB Sutopo Purwo Nugroho a wani taron da aka yi a Jakarta.
"Amma tsunami ba shi da kansa, ya kawo motoci, kaya, gidaje, ya kai ga dukan abin da ke duniya", in ji Nugroho, kuma ya ƙara da cewa kafin ya yi tasiri a gabar teku, tsunami a teku ta buɗe ya yi saurin gudu da kilomita 800 a kowace awa.
Ya ce wasu mutane sun gudu zuwa itatuwa kafin a yi ruwan.
