Ya kamata Amurka ta ninka kudaden da ake kashewa wajen samar da fasahar kere kere
Wani mai saka jari kuma masanin ilimin kere kere mai suna Kai-Fu Lee, wanda ya yi aiki a Google, Microsoft da Apple, ya ce kasar Sin ta ci gaba da kasancewa da karfi a fannin ilimin kere kere, kuma ya kamata Amurka ta ninka yawan da ta ke kashewa wajen bincike a wannan fannin.
Wannan bayani ya zo ne bayan bangarorin gwamnatin Amurka sun fitar da sanarwar AI, duk da cewa Amurka ba ta da wata dabarar kera hankali ta wucin gadi.
A shekarar da ta gabata, kasar Sin ta kaddamar da wani shiri da ta ce ta yi niyyar zama kasa da kasa a fannin kera fasahar kere kere ta AI nan da shekarar 2030.
"Bayar da kasafin kudin bincike na AI sau biyu zai zama kyakkyawan farawa, tun da sauran kasashen suna da nisa fiye da Amurka, kuma muna neman wani sabon ci gaba a AI", in ji Lee.
Lee ya bayyana a wata hira da CNBC a makon nan cewa ninka kudaden zai iya ninka yiwuwar cewa za a yi babban binciken AI na gaba a Amurka.
Lee, wanda ya wallafa littafinsa a Houghton Mifflin Harcourt a wannan watan, Superpower AI: China, Silicon Valley, and the New World Order, shi ne babban jami'in Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin AI a kasar Sin, Face++.
A Carnegie Mellon University a shekarun 1980, ya yi aiki a kan wani tsarin AI wanda ya fi na Amurka a wasan Othello, kuma daga baya ya zama babban jami'in bincike na Microsoft da shugaban ofishin Google na kasar Sin.
Lee ya yaba da gasar fasaha ta gwamnatin Amurka ta baya, kamar ta Robotics Challenge ta Hukumar Kula da Ci Gaban Ci Gaban Ci Gaban, kuma ya tambayi lokacin da za a sake yin hakan don taimakawa wajen gano sabbin masu hangen nesa.
Lee ya ce, masu bincike a Amirka suna fama sosai don su samu tallafin gwamnati.
"Ba kasar Sin ce ke janyo hankalin manyan jami'ai ba, amma kamfanoni ne", in ji Lee.
A cikin 'yan shekarun nan, Facebook da Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha suna daukar manyan masana jami'o'i don yin aiki a kan ilimin kere kere.
Lee ya ce sauye-sauyen manufofin baƙi na iya taimaka wa Amurka wajen inganta ayyukan AI.
"Ina ganin ya kamata a ba da takardar shaidar kore ga masu samun digiri a fannin AI", in ji shi.
