Ma'aikatar tsaron Amurka ta kafa Cibiyar Nazarin Artificial Intelligence a wannan shekara don shiga masana'antu da kuma masana kimiyya, kuma Fadar White House ta sanar da kafa Hukumar Nazarin Artificial Intelligence.
