Shugaba Donald Trump zai kaddamar da wani shiri na yakin neman zabe a Wheeling, West Virginia, a daren yau.
Wannan ne taro na farko a cikin taro biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
A sakamakon dakatar da zaben tabbatar da dan takararsa a kotun koli, Trump yana so ya sami goyon baya don zaben da ke tafe a tsakiyar lokacin mulkinsa, saboda 'yan Republican suna fuskantar haɗarin rasa majalisa a zaben Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a fara gabatarwar Trump a yau da dare, kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon sa a kan layi?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, a karfe 7:00 na yammacin yammacin yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a layi a ƙasa ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Trump zai yi magana game da sauraron dan takarar kotun koli Bret Kavanaugh, wanda ya faru a wannan makon kuma ya kasance mai matukar damuwa saboda zargin da ake yi game da lalata da jima'i. Ana sa ran za a dage zaben amincewa da majalisar dattijai na mako guda kafin FBI ta gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban burin wannan taron shine taimaka wa 'yan Republican su samu ci gaba kafin zaben watan Nuwamba.
A cewar Reuters, masu shirya yakin neman zaben shugaban kasar Trump sun ce wannan taro na biyar a mako mai zuwa shine don "karfafa masu sa kai da masu goyon baya don Republican su yi kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjayen da suke da su a majalisar dattawa da kuma majalisar wakilai".
"Sanar da majalisar dattawa yana da muhimmanci sosai ga tsarinsa, saboda haka shugaban zai tafi jihohi da yawa a wannan lokacin da ake da babban zango", wani mai magana da yawun Trump ya shaida wa Reuters, wanda bai so a nada shi ba.
A cewar West Virginia Metro News, masu goyon bayan daga Ohio da Pennsylvania za su iya halartar taron a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling a yau kuma za su iya sauraronsa a kafofin watsa labarai daga Pittsburgh.
A ranar Asabar, wannan ne karo na biyu da Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia a watan da ya gabata, inda ya samu sama da kashi 40 cikin dari a shekarar 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na Jam'iyyar Republican a West Virginia Patrick Morrissey wanda ya koma baya a cikin binciken.
"Ba abin mamaki ba ne ga Morrissey cewa dole ne ya zo wurin shugaban don ya taimaka masa a binciken", in ji wani masanin siyasa daga Jami'ar West Virginia, Simon Haeder, a cewar Reuters.
