Kanye West ya halarci jawabin da ya yi na neman Trump, a cikin takalminsa na sihiri, bayan ya fito a kan SNL.
Ba abin da ya yi kyau ba
Kanye West ya yi wa'azi a gidan rediyo na Saturday Night Live bayan wani mummunan aiki, inda ya yaba wa shugaban Amurka Donald Trump kuma ya ce zai tsaya takara a shekarar 2020.
Bayan ya rera waƙar ta uku a daren nan mai suna Ghost Town, wanda ya sa takalmin Make America Great Again, sai ya soma yin sallama ga 'yan Democrat kuma ya sake nuna goyon bayansa ga Shugaba Trump.
Ina yawan magana da fararen fata kuma suna cewa, "Yaya za ka so Trump, tun da yake shi ɗan wariyar launin fata ne?"
Ya ce, "Idan na damu da wariyar launin fata, da na daɗe ina ba a Amirka.
SNL ta kaddamar da wani wasan kwaikwayo na parody tare da Matt Damon a matsayin babban mutum, wanda ya nuna cewa tauraruwar Hollywood ta yi dariya game da shaidar Bret Kavanaugh a gaban kwamitin shari'a na Majalisar Dattijai game da zargin da aka yi wa Christine Blasey Ford.
Ko da yake ba a watsa shi ba, an saka hotunan West a kafofin sada zumunta ta hanyar mai zane-zane Chris Rock.
Ba a san ko Rock yana ƙoƙarin yin wa West ba'a ba.
West ya kuma yi wa masu kallo gunaguni cewa an cinye shi sosai a bango.
An yi mini barazana a baya.
Sai suka ce, "Kada ka shiga cikin wannan hatsin".
Wannan mai zalunci ne!
Sun kuma ce ina cikin wani wuri da bai dace ba, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ta ruwaito.
West ya ci gaba da cewa, "Kana son ganin wurin da bai dace ba?" kuma ya ce zai sa rigar Superman, domin hakan yana nufin ba za ka iya gaya mini abin da zan yi ba.
Ka gwada ƙauna.
Aƙalla sau biyu ne masu sauraro suka yi ihu a kan abin da ya faɗa, kuma 'yan SNL sun yi baƙin ciki, sun yi sanyin gwiwa, in ji Variety, kuma wani mutum ya ce: "Dukan ɗakin ya yi tsit.
An gayyaci West a matsayin mai maye gurbin mawaƙa Ariana Grande, wanda tsohon abokinta, rapper Mac Miller ya mutu 'yan kwanaki da suka gabata.
