Menene bikin Global Citizen Festival kuma me ya yi don rage talauci?
A ranar Asabar, za a yi bikin kiɗa na shekara-shekara na Global Citizen Festival a birnin New York, wanda ke ba da kyauta mai ban sha'awa ga taurari da kuma irin wannan aikin da zai kawo ƙarshen talauci a duniya.
A shekara ta bakwai ta bikin Global Citizen, dubban mutane za su taru a Central Park don jin daɗin ba kawai masu fasaha kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma kuma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin manufar taron, wanda shine kawo ƙarshen talauci ta 2030.
Bikin Global Citizen wanda aka kaddamar a shekarar 2012 wani ci gaba ne na Global Poverty, wata kungiya ta duniya da ke taimakawa wajen kawar da talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke yaki da ta.
Don samun tikitin kyauta na taron (idan ba ku yarda ku biya kuɗin VIP ba), baƙi sun yi jerin ayyuka ko ayyukan kamar aikin sa kai, imel ga shugaban duniya, kiran waya, ko wasu hanyoyi masu ma'ana don taimakawa wajen wayar da kan jama'a game da burin su na kawar da talauci.
Amma, yaya Global Citizen ya yi nasara shekaru 12 kafin ya kai ga abin da ya nufa?
Shin ra'ayin bayar da kyauta ta kyauta ta hanyar shawo kan mutane su nemi wani abu, ko kuma wani abu ne da ake kira clicktivism - mutanen da suke ganin cewa sa hannu kan wata takarda ta yanar gizo ko kuma su yi tweet zai kawo canji?
Global Citizen ta ce tun daga shekara ta 2011, ta samu fiye da miliyan 19 na ayyukan da magoya bayanta suka yi, suna ƙoƙarin cimma burin da suka dace.
Ya ce, waɗannan ayyukan sun sa shugabannin duniya su sanar da kudade da kuma ayyuka da suka kai dala biliyan 37 da za su shafi rayukan mutane biliyan 2.25 a shekara ta 2030.
A farkon 2018, kungiyar ta sanar da alkawuran da sanarwar 390 da suka fito daga ayyukanta, daga cikinsu akalla dala biliyan 10 sun riga sun biya ko aka tallafa musu.
Ƙungiyar ta kiyasta cewa kudade da aka tanada sun yi tasiri kai tsaye ga kusan mutane miliyan 649 a dukan duniya.
Babban alkawuran sun hada da Power of Nutrition, wani shiri na Birtaniya na masu zuba jari da kuma masu samar da kayayyaki da suka yi alkawarin taimaka wa yara su bunkasa zuwa ga iyakar damarsu, da kuma alkawarin bayar da dala miliyan 35 ga Rwanda don taimakawa wajen kawo karshen rashin abinci mai gina jiki a kasar bayan sun karbi fiye da 4,700 daga Global Citizens.
"Da taimakon gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu bayar da agaji, gwamnatoci na kasa da kuma 'yan kasa na duniya kamar ku, za mu iya yin wani abu game da rashin adalci na zamantakewa a cikin rashin abinci mai gina jiki", in ji Tracey Ullman, jakadan Power of Nutrition Project, a wani taro a wani taro na raye-raye a London a watan Afrilu na 2018.
Ƙungiyar ta kuma ce bayan fiye da 5,000 da suka yi kira ga Birtaniya ta inganta abinci mai gina jiki ga iyaye mata da yara, gwamnati ta sanar da samun kuɗi don aikin Power of Nutrition, wanda zai kai ga mata da yara miliyan 5 da ke fama da abinci mai gina jiki.
A cikin martani ga wata tambaya da ake yawan yi a shafin yanar gizonmu, "Me ya sa kake ganin za mu iya kawar da matsanancin talauci?"
Wani mai suna Global Citizen ya amsa: "Wannan zai kasance hanya mai tsawo da wahala - wani lokacin za mu kasa kuma mu kasa.
Amma kamar yadda manyan 'yancin bil'adama da kuma 'yan adawa da wariyar launin fata suka kasance a gabanmu, za mu yi nasara domin mun fi karfi tare.
