Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo mai suna World Wide Web yana shirin kaddamar da sabuwar intanet kuma ya riga Google da Facebook gaba
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo ta duniya, ya fara wani kamfani wanda ke neman ya yi gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Wani sabon shiri na wannan babban jami'in fasaha, Inrupt, wani kamfani ne da ke gina wani dandamali na Berners-Lee mai suna Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda aka adana bayanan su da kuma mutanen da suke samun damar yin amfani da su.
A wata hira da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi wa'azi cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce "mulkin duniya".
"Dole ne mu yi haka yanzu", ya ce game da wannan farawa.
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid, wadda ke ba mutane damar ƙirƙirar ɗakunan ajiya na kan layi na kansu ko POD.
Zai iya ƙunshi jerin sunayen abokan hulɗa, jerin ayyuka, kalandar, ɗakin karatu na kiɗa da sauran kayan aiki na mutum da na sana'a.
Yana kama da Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack, da Spotify suna samuwa a cikin mai bincike guda ɗaya kuma a cikin duka a lokaci guda.
Abin da ke da ban sha'awa game da ajiyar bayanai ta kan layi shi ne cewa yana da cikakken ikon mai amfani ya ƙayyade wanda zai sami damar yin amfani da wane irin bayani.
Wannan shi ne abin da kamfanin ya kira "samar da bayanai".
John Bruce, babban darektan kamfanin, ya ce manufar Inrupt ita ce ta kawo albarkatu, matakai da kuma ƙwarewar da ta dace don taimakawa dandalin Solid ya kasance ga kowa.
A halin yanzu, kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, dandamali na tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu ma'aikatan da ke aiki a kan aikin, sun yi aiki tare a kan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen aikin sa kai.
Tun daga wannan makon, masu fasahar kere kere a duniya za su iya gina nasu aikace-aikacen da ba su da tsakiya ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke shafin Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa da Facebook da Google ba sa magana game da yin wani canji na gaba daya inda duk kasuwancin su ke juyawa a daren jiya.
Ba mu nemi izinin su ba.
Berners-Lee ya rubuta a cikin wata sanarwa da ya wallafa a ranar Asabar cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu wanda zai taimaka wajen kare mutuncin da ingancin sabon shafin yanar gizon da aka gina akan dandamali na Solid.
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya sauya Intanet ta wajen kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a tattaunawar tsaka tsaki na cibiyar sadarwa.
Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da kasancewa wanda ya kafa kuma ya jagoranci World Wide Web Consortium, Web Foundation, da kuma Open Data Institute.
"Ina da tabbaci sosai game da wannan zamani na yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
