Dan wasan mai shekara 24 ya ce bai san cewa kowa yana kama da shi ba tun yana makarantar sakandare.
A kan kundi na farko na Radio 4 Desert Island Disc, wanda Lauren Laverne ya gabatar, ya ce ya yi magana da ƙarfi game da 'yancin gay don ba da damar ga wasu.
Ya kuma ce, kasancewa iyaye ya sa bai so ya ci gasar Olympics ba.
Kirsty Young, mai gabatar da shirye-shiryen ta na dogon lokaci, ta yi hutu na wata biyu saboda rashin lafiya.
Daley, wanda ya fito a matsayin mai kula da abinci a shirin farko na Lavern, ya ce ya ji ya fi kowa da ya girma tare da shi daraja, domin ba shi da kyau a amince da shi a matsayin mai son 'yan mata da maza.
Ya ce: "Har yanzu, waɗannan ra'ayoyin rashin ƙarfi da bambanci sun kasance ainihin abin da ya ba ni ƙarfi da iko na yin nasara.
Ya ce kada ya yi wa kowa rashin gaskiya idan ya gano yadda ya dace da jima'i.
Mai karɓar lambar tagulla ta Olympics sau biyu ya zama babban mai kare hakkin LGBT, kuma ya yi amfani da halartarsa a gasar Commonwealth Games na wannan shekara a Ostiraliya don ya yi kira ga ƙasashe da yawa don kawar da aikata laifuka ga 'yan luwadi.
Ya ce ya yi hakan ne domin yana jin daɗin rayuwa a sarari ba tare da wani sakamako ba kuma yana son ya ba da gudummawa ga wasu.
Dan wasan da ya lashe gasar cin kofin duniya sau uku ya ce ya yi matukar damuwa da ƙaunarsa ga mutumin da ya sadu da darektan fim din Amurka Dustin Lance Black a 2013.
Daley ya auri Oscar mai shekaru 20 da haihuwa a bara, amma ya ce bambancin shekaru bai taba zama matsala ba.
"Idan ka fuskanci irin wannan abu a wannan ƙaramin shekaru" "A gasar Olympics ta farko, yana da shekara 14 kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu shekaru uku bayan haka daga ciwon daji" "Ya ce ba shi da sauƙi a sami wani mutum a wannan shekarun da ya fuskanci irin wannan tashin hankali da kuma raguwa".
A watan Yuni, ta haifi ɗan Robert Ray Black-Daley, kuma Daley ya ce ya canja ra'ayinsa.
Idan ka tambaye ni a bara, sai ya ce, "Duk abin da na yi shi ne domin in lashe lambar zinariya".
Ka sani, akwai abubuwa da yawa fiye da lambar zinariya ta Olympics.
A gasar Olympics na, Robbie ne ya lashe lambar.
An ba shi suna bayan mahaifinsa Robert, wanda ya mutu a shekara ta 2011 yana da shekara 40 bayan an gano kansa a kwakwalwa.
Daley ya ce mahaifinsa bai yarda da cewa zai mutu ba, kuma abin da ya yi tambaya shi ne, shin sun riga sun samu tikiti zuwa gasar Olympics ta London ta 2012 domin yana son ya kasance a saman layi.
Ba zan iya gaya masa ba, ba za ku kasance a cikin layi na farko ba, Baba, ya ce.
Na riƙe hannunsa sa'ad da ya daina numfashi, kuma a lokacin da ya daina numfashi kuma ya mutu, sai na fahimci cewa ba zai yiwu a yi nasara ba, in ji shi.
Daley ya yi gasar Olympics a shekara ta 2012 kuma ya lashe tagulla.
"Na san cewa na yi mafarkin yin tsalle a gaban 'yan wasan Olympics, ban san abin da ya fi kyau ba", in ji shi.
Wannan kuma ya sa ya zaɓi waƙar farko  Fitar Heather Small  wanda ya yi magana da shi a lokacin da aka fara gasar Olympics kuma ya ci gaba da yin sa a cikinsa.
