Yana son ya halarci taron, kamar yadda kowa yake.
Mickelson ya ci rikodin Nick Fald a mafi yawan wasannin Ryder Cup da aka buga a ranar Lahadi.
Wannan zai iya nufin ƙarshen aikinsa a gasar Ryder, wadda ba ta taɓa kaiwa ga matsayin da ya kafa ba.
Mickelson ya ci nasara 18, ya yi asara 20, kuma ya yi nasara bakwai, ko da yake Furyk ya ce kasancewarsa a cikin tawagar ya kawo sakamako mai ban mamaki.
"Yana da ban dariya, mai ban dariya, mai ban dariya, mai son yin wa mutane dariya kuma babban abokin aiki ne a cikin dakin", ya bayyana.
