Kyaftin na Turai Thomas Bjorn ya san cewa manyan shugabannin za su iya ɓace ba da daɗewa ba
Thomas Bjorn, wanda ya yi aiki a matsayin kyaftin na Turai, ya san cewa babban jagora na ra'ayi na Ryder Cup na 'yan kwanaki na ƙarshe zai iya zama mai sauƙi a juya zuwa tafiya mai wuya.
Dane ya fara wasa a wasan da aka yi a shekara ta 1997 a Valderrama, inda tawagar da Captain Seve Ballesteros ya jagoranta ta kasance da fifiko a kan Amurkawa, amma suka kai ga tseren da aka yi musu da ƙarancin hasashe 141⁄2-131⁄2.
"Ya kamata ku tuna cewa a Walderram mun samu ci gaba sosai, haka nan a Brooklyn, inda muka yi asara, da kuma Walderram, inda muka yi nasara, amma a hankali", in ji Bjorn a hoto, bayan kallon yadda suka ci 5-3 a ranar Juma'a da jiya a shekarar 2018 don su jagoranci Le Golf National 10-6.
Tarihi da kuma dukan 'yan tawagar sun nuna mini cewa ba mu da wani abu a gaba.
Za ku yi sanyin gwiwa sosai gobe.
