Ronaldo ya musanta zargin da ake masa na fyade kuma lauyoyinsa sun shirya kai karar mujallar Jamus
Cristiano Ronaldo ya bayyana zargin da ake masa na yin fyade a matsayin "labari na karya" kuma ya ce mutane suna son su nuna kansu ta hanyar yin amfani da sunansa.
Lauyoyinsa suna shirin kai karar jaridar Der Spiegel ta Jamus, wadda ta ba da rahoton waɗannan zargin.
An zargi wannan dan Fotigal da kuma dan wasan Juventus da laifin yin fyade da 'yar Amurka Kathryn Mayorga a wani otal a Las Vegas a shekarar 2009.
A ranar Jumma'a ne jaridar Der Spiegel ta ruwaito cewa, an yi zargin cewa ya biya ta dala 375,000 don ta yi shiru game da lamarin.
Bayan 'yan sa'o'i bayan sanarwar zargin, Ronaldo mai shekara 33 ya yi magana a bidiyo mai rai a Instagram ga mabiyansa miliyan 142 kuma ya bayyana cewa labarin ya kasance ƙarya.
"Babu, ba, ba, ba, ba.
Abin da suka ce a yau labarai ne na karya, "in ji mai karbar lambar yabo ta zinariya a cikin kyamara.
Suna son su ciyar da kansu cikin sunana.
Wannan al'ada ce.
Suna son su zama sanannu idan sun faɗi sunana, amma wannan ɓangare ne na aikinsu.
"Ina farin ciki kuma ina lafiya", in ji mai kunnawa mai murmushi.
Rahoton Reuters ya ce lauyoyin Ronald za su kai karar jaridar Der Spiegel bisa zargin da suka yi da cewa ba a yarda da sanarwar da ake yi game da zargin da ake yi a harkar sirri ba.
Wani lauya mai suna Christian Schertz ya ce, 'yan wasan za su nemi a biya su hakkin da ya dace da laifin da suka aikata, wanda wataƙila shi ne mafi munin laifin da aka yi wa 'yancin mutum a kwanan nan.
An yi zargin cewa an yi wannan abin a watan Yuni na shekara ta 2009 a wani gidan otal din Palms Hotel da kuma gidan caca a Las Vegas.
Bayan sun hadu a gidan wasan kwaikwayo, Ronaldo da Mayorga sun koma gidan wasan kwaikwayo inda aka ce ya yi mata fyade ta ta hanyar lalata, bisa ga takardun da aka gabatar a kotun Clark County District Court a Nevada.
Mayorga ta ce bayan da aka yi zargin cewa Ronaldo ya yi laifi, ya ce mata ya yi nasara da kashi 99 cikin 100 kuma ya yi rashin nasara da kashi 1.
Takardun sun ce Ronaldo ya tabbatar da cewa ya biya domin yin jima'i, amma ya amince da hakan.
Mayorga ta kuma ce ta je ga 'yan sanda kuma ta nemi hotunan raunukanta a asibiti, amma daga baya ta amince da yin shari'a saboda tsoron ramuwa da kuma tsoron kunya.
