Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka auku a birnin Palulu da ke ƙasar Indonesia a ranar Jumma'a, kuma hukumomi sun ce ana sa ran adadin mutanen da suka mutu zai ci gaba da ƙaruwa.
Saboda rashin sadarwa, rundunar da ke taimaka wa mutane ba ta iya samun wani bayani daga yankin Donggala ba, wani yanki da ke arewacin Pala, wanda ke kusa da tsakiyar girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5.
Bayan bala'in, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga Palau.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da birnin Palu da kuma mulkin Donggala, a Sulawesi:
Palau babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya ne, wanda ke a ƙarshen ƙuƙwalwar bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, kuma an kiyasta yawan jama'arta a cikin 2017 zuwa 379,800 mutane.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin ya yi bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwarsa.
Donggala wani yanki ne na yankin da ke da nisan kilomita 300 (180 mil) a arewa maso yammacin Sulawesi.
A shekara ta 2017, birnin Regenthood, wani yanki ne na gari mai kula da gari, yana da yawan mutane 299,200.
Babban fannoni na tattalin arzikin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya shine kifi da noma, musamman a yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
Ana kuma yin amfani da nickel a lardin, amma ana yin amfani da shi sosai a Morowali, a bakin tekun Sulawesi.
Hukumar rage bala'i ta ƙasar Indonesia ta ce, a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, tsunami ya riga ya shafi birnin Pal da kuma birnin Donggala sau da yawa.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 a birnin Donggala kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje.
Tsunami ya yi wa yankin yammacin Donggala barazana a shekara ta 1996, inda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin Pacific na girgizar ƙasa da kuma girgizar ƙasa a kai a kai.
Ga jerin wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka faru a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a yammacin tekun lardin Aceh a arewacin Sumatra, Indonesia, a ranar 26 ga Disamba, ta jawo tsunami, wanda ya shafi ƙasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a lardin Aceh.
2005: Ƙarƙashin ƙasa mai ƙarfi ya afku a yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, kusa da bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudu da tsibirin Java, mafi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, kuma ta jawo tsunami da ya afkawa gabar kudu, inda ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afku kusa da Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka rasa rayukansu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai kusa da Sumatra, kuma ta jawo tsunami mai tsayi na mita 10, wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da dama kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai sauƙi ta afkawa mulkin Pidie Jaya a lardin Aceh, kuma ta haifar da lalacewa da firgici, saboda ta tunatar da mutane game da mummunan tasirin girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na 2004.
A wannan lokacin, babu tsunami, amma sama da 100 sun mutu a sakamakon rushewar gine-gine.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ƙasa ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta sa dubban masu yawon buɗe ido a cikin kurkuku na ɗan lokaci.
