Saipov, mai shekara 30, ya kai hari a kan titin keke a kan titin West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan a watan Oktoba ta amfani da wata babbar motar hayar gida da ake kira Home Depot, wadda ta yi amfani da ita wajen lalata masu tafiya da kuma masu hawa keke.
