Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi wa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Clevese, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erli, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucca rauni, zafi da rashi, an ambaci sunansa a cikin niyyar.
